snippet.title: Funny Girl Fail - Piggyback Ride Gone Terribly Wrong || Try Not To Laugh
snippet.description:
'Funny girl fail footage has surfaced from New York City, which captures the exact moment a girl found out why a cab ride is usually preferred over a piggyback ride. The funny botch occurs when the girl hops on the guy's back, causing the latter to lose balance and fall butt-first on the former's face. "We were walking in NYC and my sister tried getting a piggyback ride and you can see how that went!"
